title: PARMESAN BAKED FISH
directions: Thaw fish, if froze. Preheat oven to 450 degrees. Rinse fish; pat dry. Set aside. In a small bowl, stir together mayo, cheese, chives, adn Worcestershire sauce. Spred mayo mix over fish. Place in a greased 2qt square or rectangle baking dish. Bake 8-12 min or till fish flakes easily with a fork.
